               <item n="m_remarks_old">&lt;p&gt;This fragment contains part of the second act of the Maitreyasamitināṭaka; an Uy. parallel is MaitrHami II, 10a6-11a10. See also [[Pinault 1999]]: 195-6.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The translation and the following commentary are adapted from [[Ji et al. 1998]]: 112.&lt;/p&gt;</item>
